{"tid":2405076,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國禁播BBC世界新聞台　中大梁麗娟指象徵大於實際","createTime":"2021-02-12T06:08:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-12T06:19:35.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0219af1380917fd4eacccd02ea4e8ecdccb94dc9","tid":2405076,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T06:08:05.000Z","msg":"國家廣播電視總局通報，對英國廣播公司BBC世界新聞台，繼續在中國境內落地的新一年度申請，不予受理。中大新聞與傳播學院講師梁麗娟表示，內地通過衛星接收電視節目的人較以往少，實際影響可能是部分酒店住客，但現時旅遊業已經停頓，因此影響不是很大。<br />\n<br />\n梁麗娟分析，內地電視廣播模式已經走向式微，內地民眾都喜歡在網上獲取資訊，而BBC有透過網上發送服務，一些民眾透過虛擬私人網絡VPN去接收，海外旅客亦可用本身國家或地區的電話卡，上網接收BBC資訊，只不過不能在酒店電視收看BBC新聞，認為中方的行動象徵大於實際。<br />\n<br />\n對於香港電台不再轉播BBC部分節目，梁麗娟認為，這是跟隨內地主旋律的做法，亦是去除英國殖民地色彩的表現。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1575442-20210212.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1575442-20210212.htm&d=j8A0%2F5fiWOW2Etl1DmJ%2F%2FCfe5Xzx4ME6JwL9AZsFK0I%3D&h=e33e65f0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1575442-20210212.htm&h=a25235b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1575442-20210212.htm</a>"},{"pid":"2c9b7568f8cdda74aba2938123e5de3810894981","tid":2405076,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T06:10:13.000Z","msg":"<del>亦是去除英國殖民地色彩的表現。</del><br />\n<br />\n亦是一國一制色彩的表現 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6e4640033ce452e1f1d41659a291c0e7c1cb20b","tid":2405076,"uid":21602,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T06:15:16.000Z","msg":"台灣重睇到<br />\n所以...<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e1574f6068aecca60b5c1b3ede686598e3b2db7","tid":2405076,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a6e4640033ce452e1f1d41659a291c0e7c1cb20b","tid":2405076,"uid":21602,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"